{
  "stem": "25639.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When all of us were shaven, we looked at each other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We looked more like scarecrows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I could hardly recognize my mother anymore unless I looked straight into her blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We really looked so different.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We also, after this, received new clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "New-- I, I shouldn't have said new-- different clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had to give up all our clothing from home except for our shoes, which we were able to keep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Luckily, I had good strong shoes with me which was made for Passover by a shoemaker who made it by hand, made to order.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then came the final dehumanization, the branding.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Henceforth, I no longer had a name.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I became a number, number A6374, tattooed on my left arm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "As you see, I'm still carrying that number on my arm today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My mother was tattooed first, A6372, my sister followed with 73 and I with 74 so that we had consecutive tattoo numbers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was unusual only because, by this time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about an hour and a half later, there were hardly anybody left [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in whose families three people were still alive.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "So to have three consecutive tattoo numbers became a very unusual [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] event-- well, thing to have.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The instrument looked like a pen with an ink packet in it, probably.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It had a sharp point.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was black, I remember, and two women held our arms down and then each time this, the needle was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] put under the skin and withdrawn, the pen left a dot there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so it is that this number is made up of a whole series of dots left under the skin.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
